    dc:description "Figure 10. Afronurus rainulfiana (Braasch, 1990), larval morphology A gill V B gill VI C gill VII D bristles on the dorsal face of the hind femur E enlargement of bristles on basal part. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-D); 0.25 mm (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/895435" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1176.105159.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Afronurus rainulfiana (Braasch, 1990), female imaginal morphology A tergites I-X B anal plate C fore wing and hind wing. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/895436" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1176.105159.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Afronurus rainulfiana (Braasch, 1990), SEMs of egg morphology A general outline of egg B chorion surface between polar KCT (pKCT) and equatorial KCT (eKCT) C micropyle (M) and enlargement of eKCTs. Scale bars: 50 μm (A); 10 μm (B); 10 μm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/895437" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

